{
  "stem": "18294.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So when the Communists said, where are you?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Who you?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I said I'm Polish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they let us into Vilna, and I come back home.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then I find still my mother with my father.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My sister wasn't already there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My sister-- we had a girl living with us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She's from a very small-- very small town.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She went to school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So she lived with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when the Germans came, she said to my sister, you know what, what are you going to stay in the city?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I live in a holidays place.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Let's go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Come and stay with us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So my mother let her go.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she never came back.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Just few-- we sent some people, Polish people there, where they was living, would know about it.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So they bring us this.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This family where she was staying, this-- when the Germans arrived, they said they are Communists.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They are Communists.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So the first family what they took to shoot, there was the family where my sister were there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we never saw her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Never have heard.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And how did life change in Vilna after the Germans came and occupied?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I tell there was no life to tell because how long they stay in the German, they put us right away in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "At first, they was looking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Then they come, the Germans, in Vilna.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They took first the old men to try to take them first away to shoot them out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my father was very lucky.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We was living in a big yard, and he could run over another-- to another building, over the windows, or run away.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it was like he didn't give in to get to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
